Voiced by: Tetsu Inada (Japanese); Patrick Seitz (English)
A Hero with immense flame powers from his Quirk Hell Flame (ヘルフレイム, Heru Fureimu) who is Shouto's father, but has a strained relationship with him and the rest of his family. Following All Might's retirement, Endeavor assumes his place as the new No. 1 Hero and later becomes an internship mentor for Deku, Bakugou.
                </p>
